{
  "info": {
    "name": "Painel de Obrigações Acessórias API",
    "description": "Documentação da API REST do sistema de controle de obrigações fiscais acessórias.\n\nBase URL: http://localhost:8080\n\nTodas as respostas são envelopadas em ResponseData<T>:\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"\",\n  \"data\": { ... },\n  \"errorCode\": null\n}",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "case-e-auditoria"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:8080",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "empresaId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "obrigacaoId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET /health",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/health",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["health"]
            },
            "description": "Health check da API. Retorna 200 OK se o serviço está operacional."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Health OK",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [
                { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "text/plain" }
              ],
              "body": "Healthy"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Empresas",
      "description": "CRUD de empresas. Cada empresa pertence a um regime tributário que determina quais obrigações são geradas.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET /api/empresas",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('Resposta envelopada', () => {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json).to.have.property('success');",
                  "    pm.expect(json).to.have.property('data');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "if (pm.response.json().data && pm.response.json().data.length > 0) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('empresaId', pm.response.json().data[0].id);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/empresas?skip=0&take=50",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "empresas"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "skip", "value": "0", "description": "Registros a pular (paginação)" },
                { "key": "take", "value": "50", "description": "Registros por página (max 50)" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Lista todas as empresas com paginação."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Lista de Empresas",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [
                { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"\",\n  \"data\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"a1b2c3d4-...\",\n      \"cnpj\": \"00000000000000\",\n      \"razaoSocial\": \"Empresa Simples Nacional Ltda\",\n      \"regime\": 1,\n      \"createdAt\": \"2026-01-01T00:00:00Z\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"errorCode\": null\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "POST /api/empresas",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('Empresa criada com ID', () => {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.success).to.be.true;",
                  "    pm.expect(json.data).to.have.property('id');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('empresaId', pm.response.json().data.id);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"cnpj\": \"11222333000181\",\n  \"razaoSocial\": \"Empresa Exemplo Ltda\",\n  \"regime\": 1\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/empresas",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "empresas"]
            },
            "description": "Cria uma nova empresa. O regime tributário determina quais obrigações serão geradas (12 meses).\n\nRegimes:\n1 = Simples Nacional\n2 = Lucro Presumido\n3 = Lucro Real\n4 = Imunidade/Isenção"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Empresa Criada",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [
                { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": \"a1b2c3d4-...\",\n    \"cnpj\": \"11222333000181\",\n    \"razaoSocial\": \"Empresa Exemplo Ltda\",\n    \"regime\": 1,\n    \"createdAt\": \"2026-06-08T17:00:00Z\"\n  },\n  \"errorCode\": null\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "CNPJ Duplicado",
              "status": "Conflict",
              "code": 409,
              "header": [
                { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"CNPJ já cadastrado.\",\n  \"data\": null,\n  \"errorCode\": \"Conflict\"\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "Validação",
              "status": "Bad Request",
              "code": 400,
              "header": [
                { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"'CNPJ' não pode estar vazio; 'Razao Social' não pode estar vazia\",\n  \"data\": null,\n  \"errorCode\": \"Validation\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "GET /api/empresas/search",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('Resultados de busca', () => {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.success).to.be.true;",
                  "    pm.expect(json.data).to.be.an('array');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/empresas/search?q=simples",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "empresas", "search"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "q", "value": "simples", "description": "Termo de busca (Meilisearch typo-tolerant)" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Busca textual de empresas via Meilisearch. Suporta typo-tolerance."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Resultado da Busca",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [
                { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"\",\n  \"data\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"a1b2c3d4-...\",\n      \"cnpj\": \"00000000000000\",\n      \"razaoSocial\": \"Empresa Simples Nacional Ltda\",\n      \"regime\": 1,\n      \"createdAt\": \"2026-01-01T00:00:00Z\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"errorCode\": null\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "DELETE /api/empresas/{id}",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('Empresa deletada', () => {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.success).to.be.true;",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/empresas/{{empresaId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "empresas", "{{empresaId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Soft-delete de empresa (IsActive = false). Obrigações são deletadas via cascade da FK."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Empresa Deletada",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [
                { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"\",\n  \"data\": true,\n  \"errorCode\": null\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "Não Encontrada",
              "status": "Not Found",
              "code": 404,
              "header": [
                { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"Empresa não encontrada.\",\n  \"data\": null,\n  \"errorCode\": \"NotFound\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Obrigações",
      "description": "Gestão de obrigações acessórias: consulta, registro de entrega, histórico e exportação.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET /api/obrigacoes",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('Resposta envelopada', () => {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json).to.have.property('success');",
                  "    pm.expect(json).to.have.property('data');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "if (pm.response.json().data && pm.response.json().data.length > 0) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('obrigacaoId', pm.response.json().data[0].id);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/obrigacoes?empresaId={{empresaId}}&ano=2026&mes=6&skip=0&take=100",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "obrigacoes"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "empresaId", "value": "{{empresaId}}", "description": "ID da empresa" },
                { "key": "ano", "value": "2026", "description": "Ano da competência" },
                { "key": "mes", "value": "6", "description": "Mês da competência (1-12)" },
                { "key": "skip", "value": "0", "description": "Registros a pular (paginação)" },
                { "key": "take", "value": "100", "description": "Registros por página" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Lista as obrigações de uma empresa para um determinado mês/ano.\n\nStatus calculado automaticamente:\n- Pendente (1): data de vencimento futura, sem entrega\n- Atrasada (2): data de vencimento passada, sem entrega\n- Entregue (3): possui data de entrega"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Lista de Obrigações",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [
                { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"\",\n  \"data\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"b2c3d4e5-...\",\n      \"empresaId\": \"a1b2c3d4-...\",\n      \"razaoSocial\": \"Empresa Exemplo Ltda\",\n      \"tipo\": 1,\n      \"tipoNome\": \"DAS\",\n      \"competencia\": \"2026-06-01T00:00:00\",\n      \"dataVencimento\": \"2026-07-20T00:00:00\",\n      \"dataEntrega\": null,\n      \"status\": 1\n    }\n  ],\n  \"errorCode\": null\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "PATCH /api/obrigacoes/{id}/entrega",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('Entrega registrada', () => {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.success).to.be.true;",
                  "    pm.expect(json.data.status).to.eql(3);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"dataEntrega\": \"2026-06-08T00:00:00Z\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/obrigacoes/{{obrigacaoId}}/entrega",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "obrigacoes", "{{obrigacaoId}}", "entrega"]
            },
            "description": "Registra a entrega de uma obrigação. Se dataEntrega não for informada, usa UTC now.\n\nDispara evento de domínio ObrigacaoEntregueEvent que invalida o cache do dashboard e alertas.\n\nProteção contra concorrência via RowVersion (concurrency token do EF Core)."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Entrega Registrada",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [
                { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": \"b2c3d4e5-...\",\n    \"empresaId\": \"a1b2c3d4-...\",\n    \"razaoSocial\": \"Empresa Exemplo Ltda\",\n    \"tipo\": 1,\n    \"tipoNome\": \"DAS\",\n    \"competencia\": \"2026-06-01T00:00:00\",\n    \"dataVencimento\": \"2026-07-20T00:00:00\",\n    \"dataEntrega\": \"2026-06-08T00:00:00\",\n    \"status\": 3\n  },\n  \"errorCode\": null\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "Já Entregue",
              "status": "Conflict",
              "code": 409,
              "header": [
                { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"Obrigação já foi marcada como entregue.\",\n  \"data\": null,\n  \"errorCode\": \"Conflict\"\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "Não Encontrada",
              "status": "Not Found",
              "code": 404,
              "header": [
                { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"Obrigação não encontrada.\",\n  \"data\": null,\n  \"errorCode\": \"NotFound\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "GET /api/obrigacoes/historico/{empresaId}",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('Histórico de entregas', () => {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.success).to.be.true;",
                  "    pm.expect(json.data).to.be.an('array');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/obrigacoes/historico/{{empresaId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "obrigacoes", "historico", "{{empresaId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Retorna o histórico de obrigações já entregues por uma empresa, ordenadas da mais recente para a mais antiga."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Histórico de Entregas",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [
                { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"\",\n  \"data\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"b2c3d4e5-...\",\n      \"empresaId\": \"a1b2c3d4-...\",\n      \"razaoSocial\": \"Empresa Exemplo Ltda\",\n      \"tipo\": 1,\n      \"tipoNome\": \"DAS\",\n      \"competencia\": \"2026-06-01T00:00:00\",\n      \"dataVencimento\": \"2026-07-20T00:00:00\",\n      \"dataEntrega\": \"2026-06-08T00:00:00\",\n      \"status\": 3\n    }\n  ],\n  \"errorCode\": null\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "GET /api/obrigacoes/export",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('Content-Type é CSV', () => {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.headers.get('Content-Type')).to.include('text/csv');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/obrigacoes/export?empresaId={{empresaId}}&ano=2026&mes=6&formato=csv",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "obrigacoes", "export"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "empresaId", "value": "{{empresaId}}" },
                { "key": "ano", "value": "2026" },
                { "key": "mes", "value": "6" },
                { "key": "formato", "value": "csv", "description": "Formato de exportação: csv ou pdf" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Exporta obrigações em CSV ou PDF. O retorno é um arquivo binário (Content-Disposition: attachment)."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "CSV Export",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [
                { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "text/csv" },
                { "key": "Content-Disposition", "value": "attachment; filename=\"obrigacoes-2026-06.csv\"" }
              ],
              "body": "Tipo,Vencimento,Entrega,Status\nDAS,2026-07-20,,Pendente\nDCTF,2026-08-15,,Pendente\n"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Dashboard",
      "description": "Dashboard consolidado com totais e alertas de prazos. Dados cacheados em Redis com TTL de 30s (dashboard) e 60s (alertas).",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET /api/dashboard",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('Dashboard com totais', () => {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.success).to.be.true;",
                  "    pm.expect(json.data).to.have.all.keys('totalEmpresas', 'totalObrigacoesMes', 'pendentes', 'entregues', 'atrasadas');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "dashboard"]
            },
            "description": "Retorna os totais consolidados do dashboard para o mês corrente.\n\nDados cacheados em Redis por 30s (TTL). Cache é invalidado automaticamente quando uma obrigação é marcada como entregue."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Dashboard Data",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [
                { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"totalEmpresas\": 4,\n    \"totalObrigacoesMes\": 12,\n    \"pendentes\": 8,\n    \"entregues\": 3,\n    \"atrasadas\": 1\n  },\n  \"errorCode\": null\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "GET /api/dashboard/alertas",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
